\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This morning we\'92re finishing up our part 2 of the message and this is a tough topic but the reality is that it is a real topic and I believe that there are people in this church right now who are having very real issues with things like pornography and sex addiction and immorality to the point where they are about to make a huge mistake in their marriage or relationship and today is a sort of last effort by God to get your attention.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And at the end of the message we\'92re going to open up the alter and I want you to know that ahead of time so you can prepare your hearts for that moment\'85because my prayer is that today is a freeing day for everyone\'85not just those who are struggling with immorality but today we\'92re going to go a little deeper into what it means to even be a Christian.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But before we do that I\'92ve got to tell you what it will cost you because Jesus says that only a fool doesn\'92t count the cost.  Only a fool starts to build a house only to get half way through it and realize he doesn\'92t have enough bank to finish it.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And I believe this is where sometimes the church and myself have failed people into calling people to give up their lives for Jesus but not being clear what that means so churches are full of people who profess to know Jesus personally and think they are Christians but their life is not different than anyone else in the world\'85the look just like the world because no one ever told the cost of following Jesus.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What we are passionate about, we will purge everything else out of the way.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\
\
